data.description: You can't miss this! This gorgeous 5 bedroom / 4 bath home has so many upgrades you have to see it to believe it. Starting with the interior- SMART HOME, all new designer lighting, QUARTZ countertops, CUSTOM shelving throughout, PLANTATION shutters, marble tile front on fireplace, new sink and new fixtures in kitchen. As you enter this home, you are welcomed with a flex space that includes a WINE COOLER, electric fireplace and gorgeous Leonardo Di Vinci quartz countertop and again, more CUSTOM SHELVING. Designed as an adult beverage space but perfect for an OFFICE or FORMAL LIVING room. The upgrades continue on the exterior of this home. As you exit the interior, you are welcomed with a spacious ceramic tile patio along with beautifully designed ROCK walkway. But the Piece De Resistance is the newly built PERGOLA which is wired for ELECTRICITY and makes nights perfect for quiet relaxation or gathering with friends. This gorgeous home has a family room that boasts a Wall of Windows, a CHEFS kitchen including a DOUBLE OVEN and a bedroom and full bath ON THE MAIN. Upstairs has large 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths including the master and AN EXTRA bedroom with ANOTHER EN SUITE. This home is exquisite, and you have to see this one!
